# The error indicates that I do not have any iron ore left in my inventory to insert into the furnace. 
# I initially had 10 iron ore, but after smelting, only 7 remained, and I attempted to insert 5 without checking my current inventory.

# I need to gather more iron ore before I can continue smelting. Let's go back to the iron ore patch to harvest more iron ore.

# Moving to the nearest iron ore position to gather more.
iron_ore_position = nearest(Resource.IronOre)
move_to(iron_ore_position)  # Moving to the iron ore position
harvest_resource(iron_ore_position, quantity=10)  # Collecting more iron ore
print(f"Inventory after gathering more iron ore: {inspect_inventory()}")
